{"type":"message","id":"243783a8","parentId":"3909a54f","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:50:00.749Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a clear picture. Let me summarize the storage architecture changes from 4.23:\n\n**Before 4.23 (from openclaw.json.bak):**\n- `slots: {}` — empty, no memory slot assigned\n- `allow: []` — empty\n- No plugin entries configured\n\n**After 4.23 upgrade:**\n- `slots: { memory: \"memory-core\" }` — memory slot now explicitly assigned to memory-core\n- `allow` list populated with plugins\n- `entries` section has detailed configurations for each plugin\n- `installs` section tracks installed plugins with metadata\n\nThe key changes in 4.23:\n1. **Plugin slots system** — memory slot is now explicitly configured\n2. **Plugin allow list** — now explicitly listed what plugins are allowed\n3. **Plugin entries** — detailed per-plugin config (enabled, config, source, version, install path, etc.)\n4. **Installs registry** — tracks where each plugin was installed from\n\nStorage locations:\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/memory/` — main.sqlite, tts.sqlite, lancedb-pro/, backups/\n- `/home/halei/.openclaw/workspace/memory/` — daily memory files (DREAMS.md already moved to workspace root as DREAMS.md, and dream-log entries are in the DREAMS.md file itself)\n\nThe `.dreams/` directory mentioned in MEMORY.md doesn't actually exist - the dreams are stored in DREAMS.md file in workspace.\n\nLet me report this clearly."},{"type":"text","text":"4.23 存储架构确实变了。来看对比：\n\n## 升级前后对比\n\n| 项目 | 升级前（bak） | 升级后（4.23） |\n|------|--------------|----------------|\n| `slots.memory` | **空** | `memory-core` |\n| `plugins.allow` | **空** | 已填充 11 个插件 |\n| `plugins.entries` | 无 | 每插件独立配置 |\n| `plugins.installs` | 无 | 安装源/路径/版本记录 |\n\n## 当前存储架构\n\n```\n~/.openclaw/\n├── memory/\n│   ├── main.sqlite      ← 核心数据（69KB）\n│   ├── tts.sqlite       ← TTS 相关（69KB）\n│   ├── lancedb-pro/     ← 向量索引（已禁用 LanceDB）\n│   └── backups/\n└── workspace/memory/    ← 每日记忆文件（.md）\n```\n\n## 主要变化\n\n1. **Slot 明确化** — `slots.memory: memory-core` 现在是显式配置，不再是隐式推断\n2. **插件体系完整化** — allow 名单、entries 配置、installs 安装记录全部迁移到了新的结构\n3. **Dream 日志** — 存在 `workspace/DREAMS.md`，不再是 `.dreams/` 目录（MEMORY.md 里说的 `.dreams/` 目录实际上不存在）\n\n你现在用的是 `memory-core`（内置）+ SQLite，没有启用 LanceDB 向量存储。要开吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777164585435,"responseId":"063c942930afbc54077eb469d1b56d93"}}
