{"type":"message","id":"9f33924f","parentId":"d6cbe042","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:57:05.842Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_6eu57ddlcvya_1","toolName":"image","content":[{"type":"text","text":"This image is a screenshot of two status notifications or automated messages from a system or bot, likely within a messaging platform like Discord. The interface uses a dark mode theme.\n\nHere is a detailed breakdown of the components:\n\n### General Layout\n* **Background:** Solid dark charcoal/black.\n* **Message Style:** Two distinct messages, each contained in a dark grey rectangular bubble with rounded corners.\n* **Sender Identity:** Both messages originate from the same user or bot, indicated by an identical circular avatar on the left of each bubble. \n    * **Avatar Image:** A 3D-rendered, stylized girl with white hair and a yellow beanie decorated with small colorful pins.\n\n### Top Message Content\nThis message appears to be a log regarding a data backup process.\n* **Icon:** A green square with a white checkmark emoji (✅) at the beginning.\n* **Text (First Part):** \"每日备份完成\\n\" — This translates to \"Daily backup complete.\" Notably, it contains a literal \"backslash n\" (`\\n`), which is a coding character for a new line that didn't render as an actual line break in this interface.\n* **Icon:** A brown cardboard box emoji (📦).\n* **Text (Second Part):** \" 备份 → 已推送至 openclaw-backup\" — This translates to \"Backup → has been pushed to openclaw-backup.\"\n\n### Bottom Message Content\nThis message appears to be a log regarding the completion of a specific software script or task.\n* **Icon:** A double helix DNA emoji (🧬).\n* **Text:** \"Capability Evolver 完成 (exit 0)\"\n    * **\"Capability Evolver\":** The name of the process or program in English.\n    * **\"完成\":** Chinese for \"Finished\" or \"Complete.\"\n    * **\"(exit 0)\":** A technical command-line term indicating that a program has successfully completed its task without any errors.\n\n### Summary\nThe image depicts automated logs confirming that two separate tasks—a daily data backup to a location called \"openclaw-backup\" and a process named \"Capability Evolver\"—have both finished successfully."}],"details":{"model":"minimax/MiniMax-VL-01","image":"/home/halei/.openclaw/media/inbound/fc7a9e5c-af94-439f-9153-f6c0d75a3bb7.jpg","attempts":[]},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777165025842}}
{"type":"message","id":"e854831d","parentId":"9f33924f","timestamp":"2026-04-26T00:57:09.290Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The image shows two Discord notifications:\n1. Daily backup complete → pushed to openclaw-backup\n2. Capability Evolver completed (exit 0)\n\nSo the backup IS working and has been running. But the issue I identified is that `workspace/memory/` is not being backed up. Let me address that while also acknowledging the image."},{"type":"text","text":"看到了，备份每天凌晨3点都在跑，Capability Evolver 也正常。\n\n但问题还是那个——`workspace/memory/`（你的每日记忆文件）没有进备份。要加吗？改一行就行：\n\n```bash\n# 在 backup.sh 里加一行\ndo_rsync \"$OPENCLAW_DIR/workspace/memory/\" \"workspace/memory/\"\n```\n\n加完明天凌晨3点自动生效。要我改吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777165025844,"responseId":"063c95e2c19e5a236f08bfaa39c5f47a"}}
